    />
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8 pr-4">
    <div class="w-full border-t border-stone-200 border-dashed">
      <h4 class="mt-4 !text-lg">1. Open source</h4>
      <p class="!text-sm text-slate-light">
        Inspect the code, run your own scans, and verify what’s running.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full border-t border-stone-200 border-dashed">
      <h4 class="mt-4 !text-lg">2. Self-host & sovereignty</h4>
      <p class="!text-sm text-slate-light">
        Self-host on your own infra, keep data in-country, and run in air-gapped
        networks.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full border-t border-stone-200 border-dashed">
      <h4 class="mt-4 !text-lg">3. Zero-Touch Data</h4>
      <p class="!text-sm text-slate-light">
        Connect Postgres/MySQL/SQL Server (and more) - and we won’t hold your
        data.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full border-t border-stone-200 border-dashed">
      <h4 class="mt-4 !text-lg">4. Free SSO and custom RBAC</h4>
      <p class="!text-sm text-slate-light">
        Unlike competitors, we provide SSO and custom RBAC for free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<CustomerQuotes />

<hr class="w-1/3 my-12 mx-auto text-ivory-dark border-dashed" />
